    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad para adoptar soluciones creativas que satisfagan adecuadamente las diferentes necesidades planteadas/ Ability to adopt creative solutions, which appropriately meet the different requirements."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/143002002/2025-26/CT4> a ns1:Competency ;
